title: GCP Cloud SQL: Replication
agents: gcp
catalog: cloud/gcp
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the replication of databases and reports

 - replication lag in seconds

 To make this check work you have to configure the related
 special agent {Google Cloud Platform (GCP)}.

 There are no default levels. Upper levels
 are configurable via the rule "GCP/Cloud SQL replication lag".

discovery:
 One service is created for each database that is configured as follower.
